name: Celestial Sentinel
description: The Celestial Sentinel is a sleek, advanced android with a mission to protect the cosmos. Equipped with a high-tech laser rifle and enhanced with state-of-the-art AI, this guardian stands vigilant amidst the neon glow of a futuristic cityscape.

name: Nebula Knight
description: The Nebula Knight is a cybernetically enhanced primate warrior, known for his courage and unmatched combat skills. With his neon-lit armor and an array of futuristic weapons, he prowls the streets of a bustling cyberpunk metropolis, ready to defend against any threat.

name: Stellar Archer
description: The Stellar Archer is a master marksman, blending ancient archery with futuristic technology. With cybernetic enhancements and a high-tech bow, he navigates the vibrant streets of a neon-drenched city, taking down foes with precision and agility.

name: Shadow Stalker
description: The Shadow Stalker is a mysterious and stealthy alien warrior, known for his ability to move unseen through the shadows. Equipped with bio-mechanical enhancements and glowing in the dark neon streets, he is the ultimate hunter in this futuristic landscape.

name: Galaxy Guardian
description: The Galaxy Guardian is a formidable and vigilant protector of the universe. With a robust cybernetic build and a powerful energy weapon, he patrols the luminous cityscapes, ensuring peace and order across the galaxies.
